### Books - Category Operations
### Environment variables from ../environments.env

@baseUrl = {{$dotenv baseUrl}}
@apiUrl = {{$dotenv apiUrl}}

###
### Get Books by Category - Programming
GET {{apiUrl}}/books/category/programming
Content-Type: application/json

###
### Get Books by Category - Software Architecture
GET {{apiUrl}}/books/category/software-architecture
Content-Type: application/json

###
### Get Books by Category - Interview Preparation
GET {{apiUrl}}/books/category/interview-preparation
Content-Type: application/json

###
### Get Books by Category - Web Development
GET {{apiUrl}}/books/category/web-development
Content-Type: application/json

###
### Get Books by Category - Data Science
GET {{apiUrl}}/books/category/data-science
Content-Type: application/json

###
### Get Books by Category - Fiction
GET {{apiUrl}}/books/category/fiction
Content-Type: application/json

###
### Get Books by Category with Pagination
GET {{apiUrl}}/books/category/programming?page=1&limit=3
Content-Type: application/json

###
### Get Books by Category with Sorting
GET {{apiUrl}}/books/category/programming?sortBy=rating&sortOrder=desc
Content-Type: application/json

###
### Get Available Books Only in Category
GET {{apiUrl}}/books/category/programming?availableOnly=true
Content-Type: application/json

###
### Get Books by Non-existent Category (Error Test)
GET {{apiUrl}}/books/category/nonexistent-category
Content-Type: application/json

###
### Get Popular Books by Category
GET {{apiUrl}}/books/category/programming/popular
Content-Type: application/json

###
### Get Recently Added Books by Category
GET {{apiUrl}}/books/category/programming/recent
Content-Type: application/json

###
### Get Top Rated Books by Category
GET {{apiUrl}}/books/category/programming/top-rated
Content-Type: application/json

###
### Get Books by Category with Rating Filter
GET {{apiUrl}}/books/category/programming?minRating=4.5
Content-Type: application/json

###
### Get Books by Multiple Categories
GET {{apiUrl}}/books/categories?categories=programming,software-architecture
Content-Type: application/json